WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.450 align:middle line:90%


00:00:09.450 --> 00:00:12.390 align:middle line:84%
>> Did you know that within
our bodies we have a fountain

00:00:12.390 --> 00:00:13.410 align:middle line:90%
of youth?

00:00:13.410 --> 00:00:15.660 align:middle line:84%
The mechanics of
telomere growth offers

00:00:15.660 --> 00:00:20.700 align:middle line:84%
us insight on how we can
create a long-lived biology.

00:00:20.700 --> 00:00:23.955 align:middle line:10%
I'm your host, Bruce Lipton, for
this series on Inner Evolution.

00:00:23.955 --> 00:00:26.820 align:middle line:90%
