experiments, they found

00:24:17.670 --> 00:24:21.630 align:middle line:84%
that every time the
new moon was present,

00:24:21.630 --> 00:24:24.640 align:middle line:90%
the snails behavior went 50-50.

00:24:24.640 --> 00:24:27.450 align:middle line:84%
So the first thing they
thought of, well, the moon

00:24:27.450 --> 00:24:29.050 align:middle line:90%
