00:24:29.050 --> 00:24:32.970 align:middle line:84%
So what they did was create
an artificial gravity

00:24:32.970 --> 00:24:34.770 align:middle line:90%
underneath the snails.

00:24:34.770 --> 00:24:37.320 align:middle line:84%
And at the time of
the new moon, they

00:24:37.320 --> 00:24:41.190 align:middle line:84%
rotated this artificial
gravity 180 degrees off

00:24:41.190 --> 00:24:43.530 align:middle line:90%
from the normal orientation.

00:24:43.530 --> 00:24:44.850 align:middle line:90%
And guess what?

00:24:44.850 --> 00:24:48.390 align:middle line:84%
When they created an artificial
gravity and moved it,

00:24:48.390 --> 00:24:51.660 align:middle line:84%
then the snails then
continue to go to the right.

00:24:51.660 --> 00:24:53.280 align:middle line:90%
The point was very clear.

00:24:53.280 --> 00:24:55.770 align:middle line:84%
The behavior of
the snail is tied

00:24:55.770 --> 00:24:58.240 align:middle line:90%
to the gravity of the planet.

00:24:58.240 --> 00:25:00.480 align:middle line:84%
But the gravity of
the planet is altered

00:25:00.480 --> 00:25:02.180 align:middle line:90%
by the movement of the moon.

00:25:02.180 --> 00:25:03.780 align:middle line:90%
The net result is this.

00:25:03.780 --> 00:25:09.120 align:middle line:84%
Then the moon's phase determined
the behavior of the snail.

00:25:09.120 --> 00:25:11.790 align:middle line:84%
Well, that's a
scientific understanding

00:25:11.790 --> 00:25:15.300 align:middle line:84%
